event_text: Collective exhibition of works on paper, which are part of the funds of the Gallery. Until today, they have been rarely exhibited. Becoming in this way a "new Fund", formed by drawings of artists such as: Alfredo Alcaín, Dis Berlin, Carlos Swartz, Estrada, Simeón Saiz Ruíz, José María Sicilia, Joan Cardells, Lluís Lleó, Eduard Arbós, or Perdro Moreno Meyerhoff...
